description: Channel Islands airline Blue Islands cancels its services to London Southend and Liverpool.
title: Flybe partner cancels two 'unsustainable' Guernsey-UK routes
title_page: Flybe partner cancels two 'unsustainable' Guernsey-UK routes - BBC News
maintext: Mr Veron said the airline was "committed to serving the communities of Guernsey and Jersey", but suspending the routes was "vital for the health of the wider business".
